- cs.SD (Sound) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of emojis in vocabulary analysis, which can be considered a form of non-verbal communication.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possibility as the paper discusses the potential use of the identified proxy of socio-economic status in smart cities to provide better services to the community members.
- cs.SOC (Social and Economic Networks) is also a possibility as the paper deals with identifying a proxy of socio-economic status and its potential applications in healthcare and smart cities.
